{"tid":194601,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"今朝答地鐵返工 比後面個呀嬸鬧:-(","createTime":"2017-04-10T05:44:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T06:23:43.000Z","uid":100861,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e96f6a88a4cac453a81b3782322289d0fcc1399e","tid":194601,"uid":100861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T05:44:19.000Z","msg":"我本身就排隊排係最前個位 後面愈黎愈多人排隊<br />\n架車到 咁我就行埋左少少讓中間條路出黎比人落車<br />\nd人慢慢咁落 咁愈黎愈多人係果個位 我繼續企係到唔行 想等所有人落晒車先入<br />\n我都已經聽到後面有d&quot;吱吱&quot;聲 我心諗應該係等上車唔耐煩 所以係到&quot;吱&quot;人<br />\n之後d人落得七七八八 有少少位出左黎 但係未落晒所有人 我後面個呀嬸就推開左我 衝左上車 <br />\n最後 所有人落晒車 我就上車 企左係果個呀嬸附近 <br />\n佢無啦啦就係到鬧: 阻q住晒 唔上車 唔好阻住條路 你唔趕時間人地趕時間<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我無理到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6308fd3233d47b922c4ac00f5fd666287c52e5ac","tid":194601,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T05:45:55.000Z","msg":"佢都戇撚鳩, 上遲上早咪又同一班地鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"833927c3fde5af41870549f2265b34becb76a520","tid":194601,"uid":100861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T05:47:21.000Z","msg":"我覺得我無做錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但都要比人鬧"},{"pid":"844404de713eda0113496e58c5ba62ecb0ad80ac","tid":194601,"uid":23902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T05:58:14.000Z","msg":"廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c99ac4c489352d61e4d45f18df4ef55e62945fc1","tid":194601,"uid":24775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T06:18:18.000Z","msg":"先落後上是常識吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4